Welcome to Elanco

Elanco is a global leader in animal health dedicated to innovating and delivering products and services to prevent and treat disease in farm animals and pets, creating value for farmers, pet owners, veterinarians, stakeholders, and society as a whole.

Elanco’s Breakthrough Treatment for Deadly Canine Parvovirus Has Saved Thousands of Puppies, Reaffirms Commitment to Increasing the Availability of Canine Parvovirus Monoclonal Antibody for Second Annual National Parvo Awareness Day

Read More

Elanco Sells Royalty and Milestone Rights for Lotilaner in Human Health to Blackstone; Accelerates Debt Paydown

Read More

Elanco Animal Health Reports First Quarter 2025 Results

Read More

Global Inclusion, Diversity, Equity & Accessibility (IDEA)

Elanco strives to foster the inclusion of all employees, customers and stakeholders around the world, and celebrate the diversity of its individuals.

Learn More

Our Products & Services

At Elanco, we create innovative solutions through our products and services that address the challenges of an ever-changing world and empower those who raise and care for animals.

Read More

Elanco's Healthy Purpose™/ESG

Elanco's Healthy Purpose™ advances the well-being of animals, people and the planet, to realize our vision of Food and Companionship Enriching Life.

  • Healthier Animals
  • Healthier People
  • Healthier Planet
  • Healthier Enterprise
Explore our Healthy Purpose™

Leading Through Innovation

Elanco's research and development process applies expertise and data-driven insights to create solutions to the most significant animal health challenges.

Read More

Careers at Elanco

Join our team of engaged and purpose-driven employees, and learn how you can make a difference at Elanco.

Read About Careers

You Might Be Interested In

Get to know Elanco, our hiring process and our people’s contributions to the well-being of animals.

Our Story

Explore our six decades of innovating and nurturing relationships to become a global animal health leader.

Read More

Purpose-Driven Culture

Our vision - Food and Companionship Enriching Life - guides the higher purpose we serve. Learn more about how it differentiates us and shapes our daily work.

Read More

Our People

Our people’s desire to make a difference drives innovation, challenges status quo, and helps tackle tough issues as a team.

Read More

styles: #consent_blackbar {   	position:fixed;    bottom:0;    z-index:999999;    width: 100vw;    background: transparent;    pointer-events: none;}  /* #teconsent {    position:fixed;    bottom:10px;    z-index:999999;  }  */#truste-consent-track {    /* margin-bottom: 100vh; */    pointer-events: all;}#consent_blackbar > a {    bottom: 0;    position: absolute;    pointer-events: all;}    .truste-banner {       margin: 0 auto;       }    .truste-messageColumn {        font-family: Fira-sans,sans-serif;        font-size: 14px;        color: #004267;        margin: 15px 0px 15px 5px;        float: left;        width: 100%;        text-align: center;    }    .truste-buttonsColumn { float:right; margin: 10px 0px 10px 0px; text-align: center; float: none; padding-top: 3em; }.truste-button1     {        font-family: Fira-sans,sans-serif;        background: grey;        color: #fff;        font-size: 14px;        min-width: 170px;        height: auto;        cursor: pointer;        margin-left: 5px;    	padding:5px;        border: 0px none;transform: skew(-10deg);    }    .truste-button2  {        font-family: Fira-sans,sans-serif;        background: #0072CE;        color: #fff;        font-size: 14px;        min-width: 170px;        height: auto;        cursor: pointer;        margin-left: 5px;    	padding:5px;        border: 0px none;transform: skew(-10deg);    }  .truste-button1:hover, .truste-button2:hover{          background:#004267;        }	  .truste-button3  {        font-family:  Fira-sans,sans-serif;        font-size: 12px;        width: 140px;        height: auto;        cursor: pointer;        margin-left: 5px;    	padding:5px;        color: #00559c;    	border: none;    	background-color: transparent;    	outline: none;    }     .hidedesktop {		display: none;        font-family:  Fira-sans,sans-serif;        font-size: 14px;        cursor: pointer;        color: #00559c;    	text-decoration:none;	}  .truste-cookie-link {        font-family:  Fira-sans,sans-serif;        font-size: 12px;        cursor: pointer;        color: #004267;    	text-decoration:underline;    display:inline-block;            padding: 5px;  }  .truste-cookie-link:hover  {    color:#0072CE;  }        /* MEDIA QUERIES */      @media screen and (max-width: 627px) {      .truste-cookie-link {    width: 100%;      }    .truste-banner {       margin: 0 10px;      }        .truste-messageColumn, .truste-buttonsColumn {        float: left;        width: 100%;      }            .truste-messageColumn {       margin: 15px 0px 10px 0px;      }                .truste-buttonsColumn {float:right;          margin: 10px 0px 10px 0px;    text-align: center;    float: none;    padding-top: 3em;      }                      .truste-button1,      .truste-button2 {        margin-top: 5px;        margin-left: 0px;       	width: 100%;      }    	.truste-button3 {        display: none;      }    	.hidedesktop {		display: inline;        font-size: 14px;        cursor: pointer;        color: #00559c;    	text-decoration:none;	}    }      @media screen and (max-width: 686px) {      .truste-button1 {        padding: 5px 8px;      }            .truste-cookie-link {        padding: 0;      }    }    	@media screen and (min-width: 628px) and (max-width: 856px) {      .truste-cookie-link {    width: 34%;        padding: 0;      }    .truste-banner {       margin: 0 10px;      }        .truste-messageColumn, .truste-buttonsColumn {        float: left;        width: 100%;      }            .truste-messageColumn {       margin: 15px 0px 10px 0px;      }                .truste-buttonsColumn {       margin: 10px 0px 10px 0px;      }      .truste-button1,    .truste-button2 {        margin-top: 0px;        margin-left: 0px;       	width: 32%;        float:left;      }            .truste-button2 {        margin-right:5px;      }      	.truste-button3 {        display: none;      }    	.hidedesktop {		display: inline;        font-size: 14px;        cursor: pointer;        color: #00559c;    	text-decoration:none;	}      }
